-- Lonmin Mine Violence Death Total Yet to Be Verified, Mnisi Says
-- B y   M a t t h e w   H i l l
-- 2012-08-16T19:45:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-16/lonmin-mine-violence-death-total-yet-to-be-verified-mnisi-says.html
The number of people who died as
police dispersed striking miners near  Lonmin Plc (LMI) ’s Marikana
platinum mine in South Africa today is yet to be verified, Zweli
Mnisi, a spokesman for the country’s police ministry, said in a
text message today.  In an earlier interview Mnisi said at least 18 people had
died.  To contact the reporter on this story:
